message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this exceptional product. I believe it will bring significant value to you. I am offering it to you at a price of $1200000.

Hi Alice, thank you for the offer. While I see the value in your product, my budget is limited. I would like to offer you $800000 for it. I believe this is a fair price considering my budget constraints.
Hi Bob, I understand your budget constraints, but this product offers significant value that I believe is worth more. How about we meet somewhere in the middle? I can offer it to you for $1000000.
